sentences: David Freeman is a British singer, musician and songwriter, best known for being a member of the new wave duo The Lover Speaks during the 1980s.
Freeman was born in Ilford, Essex, on 25 September 1957 and moved to Coventry at the age of 15.
In 1976, the band evolved into the punk group The Flys, with Freeman providing guitar and vocals.
The band recorded a number of singles, two EPs; Bunch of Fives (1977) and Four From the Square (1980), and two studio albums; Waikiki Beach Refugees (1978) and Own (1979).
